# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Build Outputs
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Compiled binaries
/bin/
/dist/
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# Test binaries
*.test

# Output of `go build`
/main

